      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know... i should talk to someone. it's just that talking feels so useless. like, what's the point of explaining how much it hurts when nothing actually changes? the house is just so quiet now. it feels like the light has just been sucked out of everything. it's not even a sharp pain anymore, it's just this heavy, empty nothingness. it feels more real than anything else right now.",
